[00:00.43]Луги - SadSvit/Do Sliz
[00:01.15]TME享有本翻译作品的著作权
[00:01.15]Lyrics by：Bohdan Rozvadovskyi/Kateryna Zakrevska
[00:02.17]   
[00:02.17]Composed by：Bohdan Rozvadovskyi
